#
# NOTE: vmem scatter_release is specific to the V66 to address a V60/V61 pipeline issue where an 
# explicit release was required to avoid a scatter storage hazard.  These vmem instructions were 
# a microarchitectural workaround that existed only for V60‑class cores and was never part of the 
# stable, forward‑compatible HVX ISA. 
